comments: Lillard (POR) establishes himself in a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area prior to the contact with Westbrook (OKC).
Ferguson (OKC) makes marginal contact with Lillard's (POR) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Westbrook (OKC) makes marginal contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.
George (OKC) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) briefly places his arm around Grant's (OKC) back during the screen, but immediately slides it off without restricting his FOM.
George (OKC) sets the screen on Aminu (POR) and does not give him room to avoid the contact.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with Grant (OKC) during his shot attempt near the basket.  McCollum's arms are not vertical, but he avoids making contact with Grant's arms.
Westbrook (OKC) dislodges Harkless (POR) from his rebounding position.
Curry (POR) makes incidental contact with George (OKC) that does not cause him to lose control of his dribble.
George (OKC) legally contests McCollum's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Ferguson (OKC) briefly grasps Lillard's (POR) right arm and releases off ball.
Harkless (POR) and George (OKC) briefly engage and disengage.
McCollum (POR) briefly grasps George's (OKC) arm but disengages without restricting his FOM during the pick.
Harkless (POR) and George (OKC) briefly engage and disengage.
George (OKC) releases from the contact and does not extend his arm into Harkless (POR) to create space.
Westbrook (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RAR shows George (OKC) jumps vertically and legally contests the driving shot attempt by Lillard (POR).
LAR shows Aminu (POR) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Westbrook (OKC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) briefly grasps Ferguson's (OKC) jersey and releases.  The two players make incidental contact with each other that causes them to fall to the floor.
Lillard (POR) makes a legal move after his gather.
George (OKC) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
